Generated Narrative: ImplementationGuide ch.fhir.ig.ch-epreg

CH_EPREG

The official URL for this implementation guide is: 

http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epreg/ImplementationGuide/ch.fhir.ig.ch-epreg

FHIR implementation guide for the pregnancy passport in Switzerland.

name: CH_EPREG
title: CH EPREG (R4)
description: FHIR implementation guide for the pregnancy passport in Switzerland.

extension.valueMarkdown: Automatically added as a dependency - all IGs depend on the HL7 Extension Pack

resource.name: CH EPREG Composition
resource.description: This profile constrains the Composition resource to represent the the first entry in the CH EPREG Document.

resource.name: CH EPREG Coverage
resource.description: This profile constrains the Coverage resource to represent the insurance data.

resource.name: CH EPREG Document
resource.description: This profile constrains the Bundle resource to represent the pregnancy passport.

resource.name: CH EPREG Encounter: Child
resource.description: This profile constrains the Encounter resource to represent a pregnancy visit from the child's perspective.

resource.name: CH EPREG Encounter: Mother
resource.description: This profile constrains the Encounter resource to represent a pregnancy visit from the mother's perspective.

resource.name: CH EPREG Extension: Note
resource.description: This extension represents a comment.

resource.name: CH EPREG Extension: Number
resource.description: This extension represents the number, for example, the number of the visit or an examination (e.g. ultrasound).

resource.name: CH EPREG Extension: Planned Next Pregnancy Visit
resource.description: This extension represents the planned next pregnancy visit.

resource.name: CH EPREG Extension: Primary Contact
resource.description: This extension represents if it is the primary contact.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Base): Pregnancy Progress
resource.description: This base profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the pregnancy progress.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Base): Results Laboratory
resource.description: This base profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the laboratory results.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Child): Fetal Heart Feature
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the fetal heart feature (e.g. rate, sounds, rhythm).

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Child): Fetal Movement
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the movement of the fetus (e.g. activity, strength).

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Child): Fetal Position
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the position of the fetus.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Lab): Blood Group
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the blood group.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Lab): Fetal RhD
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the fetal Rhesus D determination from the maternal blood.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Abdominal Circumference
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the birth abdominal circumference.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Blood Pressure
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the blood pressure.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Body Weight
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the body weight.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Fundus Height
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the the height of the gravid uterus.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Gestational Age in Days
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the gestational age in days.

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Urine Finding
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the findings of the urine dipstick test (e.g. protein, glucose, nitrite, bacteria).

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Vagina Feature
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the vagina feature (e.g. cervix, cervical os).

resource.name: CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Weight Gain
resource.description: This profile constrains the Observation resource to represent the gestational weight gain.

resource.name: CH EPREG Organization: Treating Healthcare Provider
resource.description: This profile constrains the Organization resource to represent the treating healthcare provider.

resource.name: CH EPREG Patient: Child
resource.description: This profile constrains the Patient resource to represent the child (fetus/newborn). (See also the [IBCM Fetal Record Profile](https://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ibcm/2024Sep/StructureDefinition-ibcm-fetal-record.html).)

resource.name: CH EPREG Patient: Mother
resource.description: This profile constrains the Patient resource to represent the pregnant individual.

resource.name: CH EPREG Practitioner: Treating Healthcare Provider
resource.description: This profile constrains the PractitionerRole resource to represent the treating healthcare provider.

resource.name: CH EPREG PractitionerRole: Treating Healthcare Provider
resource.description: This profile constrains the PractitionerRole resource to represent the treating healthcare provider.

resource.name: CH EPREG RelatedPerson: Mother
resource.description: This profile constrains the RelatedPerson resource to represent the relationship between the mother and the child.

resource.name: CH EPREG RelatedPerson: Parent
resource.description: This profile constrains the RelatedPerson resource to represent the relationship between the parent (besides the biological mother) and the child.

resource.name: CH EPREG VS: Blood Group
resource.description: This value set includes SNOMED CT codes for blood group findings.

resource.name: CH EPREG VS: Fetal Position
resource.description: This value set includes SNOMED CT codes for fetal positions.

resource.name: CH EPREG VS: Fetal RhD Antigen
resource.description: This value set includes LOINC codes for the fetal Rhesus D determination.

resource.name: CH EPREG VS: Parent
resource.description: This value set includes SNOMED CT codes for the type of parent.
